### Filament Modal Example
```php
// Filament Action with Modal
public static function table(Table $table): Table
{
    return $table
        ->actions([
            Action::make('edit')
                ->modal()
                ->form([
                    TextInput::make('name')
                        ->required(),
                ])
                ->action(function (array $data) {
                    // Handle form submission
                }),
        ]);
}
```

